  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Grand Hotel Belvedere is on a Bed &amp; Breakfast basis, with an optional upgrade to half board. </p>
<p>Each morning a varied breakfast buffet is available, with a classic continental offering and daily hot options. </p>
<p>If you have opted for half board, you can enjoy a five-course evening meal with a choice of main. </p>
<p>The hotel has two restaurants. Restaurant Waldrand serves classic Swiss specialty dishes, while Brasserie Belvedere serves hearty bistro style meals.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
