  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are around 20-25m² sleeping two people with a double or twin beds. Choose between a room with views of the Jungfrau or the hotel gardens and forest. Both Garden View and Jungfrau View rooms have either a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>are around 24-29m² sleeping two people with a double or twin beds. Choose between a room with views of the hotel garden and forests, or the Jungfrau. Both Garden View and Jungfrau View rooms have a bathroom or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are around 29m² sleeping two to three people. These rooms have double or twin beds, and an additional sofa bed for the third person - either one child or one adult. Choose between a garden forest view or Jungfrau view. Both Garden View and Jungfrau View rooms have a bathroom with bathtub.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twin or double beds. Please specify your choice at the time of booking.</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>WC</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
